Implement getCliForModel(model: string):
1. Get provider via getModelProvider(model)
2. If provider is 'anthropic', return { cli: 'claude', reason: 'anthropic-native' }
3. If ccr is installed (isCcrInstalled()), return { cli: 'ccr', reason: 'ccr-available' }
